		{"id":"architecture-todo","type":"text","text":"## 待补\n\n- 分布式系统基础（CAP / BASE / 一致性）\n- 微服务 vs 单体取舍\n- 系统设计模板（IM / Feed / 短链 / 评论 / 秒杀）","x":330,"y":2320,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"backend-todo","type":"text","text":"## 后端基础待补\n\n- GraphQL / RPC / 鉴权与会话\n- 限流 / 重试 / 幂等 / 熔断\n- Node 服务端 & BFF 进阶\n- Redis / MQ\n- IaC / GitOps / 平台工程","x":330,"y":1940,"width":280,"height":230,"color":"6"},
